When they insisted on whether Jesus would have been in favor, he laughed and said that Jesus is too smart to run for office.
The human race remains unusually open to everything.
Huckabee’s rise in Iowa coincides with the recent prodigious grant research by libertarian Ron Paul, and hissing during Wednesday’s debate.
